Icintu ciletelezya kukondwa kapati akataa baabo basyomeka kubala Bbaibbele ncilongwe cili akataa Yahushua a Banakristu mumasimpe aakuti boonse bakazyalwa kuli Yahuwah. Munzila iilaa mulimo, Banakristu balagwasyigwa canguzu kapati mukukakatila kwabo kuti batazumanani kukkala buumi bwa cinyonyoono. Baleembelwa cakuyandigwa akukwabililwa aa Yahushua muzeki wa buntu bwaansi, kuzwa kuli dyabooli. Yahushua lwakwe wakaletwa aa Yahuwah mubuumi buno munzila yaandeene. Ma, coonse eeci ceelede kutukkazyika
..........
